<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="plan-n">plan <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /plæn/    美 /plæn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[常用复数] 图样；平面图：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The architect is drawing up <strong>plans for</strong> the new offices. 
建筑师正在绘制新办公楼的设计图。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>计划；打算；方案：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We need to <strong>make plans for</strong> the future.
我们必须规划未来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are no <strong>plans to</strong> build new offices.
目前没有建新办公楼的计划。</p></div></div>